1.caption: Signal House residents move in at Christmastime. Unlimited flirting equals love at the speed of light! Can the brazen new celebrity panel predict the future?

2.caption: Better not blink because this love triangle is heating up fast! Two men, two fierce plans to woo Ji-hyeon -- but who will win her heart and that sunny smile?

3.caption: We're all drawn to a humble, hard-working man. But with zero votes, Cupid has yet to visit Ui-dong. Meanwhile, the guys get a surprise mission: date journals!
